# Alex Marshall

> Alex Marshall is a humanistic counsellor and artist based in London, supporting people through deep personal change.

Alex is a former Silicon Valley founder turned humanistic counsellor and artist. He grew up across four countries (Mexico, the US, Spain, and England) and speaks multiple languages. He previously co-founded Twingate and worked at Dropbox and Bloomberg.

